  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  diagnosis of Dermatomyositis ore polymyositis according to the International Myositis
             Assessment and Clinical Studies Group

          -  functional impairment (an HAQ score greater than 0.5)

          -  stability of muscle impairment

          -  medical insurance

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  no recent inflammatory activity

          -  other chronic disease

          -  cognitive impairment

          -  patients who participated to a rehabilitation program before inclusion
      </textblock>
